# Mobile PWA UX

- Account for mobile-first PWA behavior.
- Check safe-area insets, dynamic viewport height, keyboard behavior, bottom overlap, horizontal overflow, and map/suggestions overlays.
- Keep mobile UI compact.
- Avoid layout changes that make iOS/Android PWA behavior worse.
- Address selection/autocomplete UI must not cause page jumps or overflow.
